<para>Detailed documentation for the exp_mc20 event class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
    </detaileddescription>
    <programlisting>
<codeline lineno="1"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="2"><highlight class="comment">/**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="3"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@file<sp/>event.dox</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="4"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Detailed<sp/>documentation<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>exp_mc20<sp/>event<sp/>class.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="5"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@page<sp/>exp_mc20_event_page<sp/>exp_mc20<sp/>Event</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>exp_mc20_event_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>specialization<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>and<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>handle<sp/>events<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>experimental<sp/>Monte<sp/>Carlo<sp/>simulation<sp/>for<sp/>Run<sp/>3<sp/>(MC20).<sp/>It<sp/>defines<sp/>the<sp/>structure<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event,<sp/>including<sp/>the<sp/>particles<sp/>and<sp/>their<sp/>relationships,<sp/>and<sp/>provides<sp/>methods<sp/>for<sp/>building<sp/>and<sp/>compiling<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>input<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>exp_mc20_event_class<sp/>The<sp/>exp_mc20<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>class<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>and<sp/>implements<sp/>its<sp/>virtual<sp/>methods<sp/>to<sp/>provide<sp/>event-specific<sp/>functionality.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>exp_mc20_event_ctor<sp/>Constructor<sp/>and<sp/>Destructor</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`exp_mc20()`:<sp/>The<sp/>constructor<sp/>initializes<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>by<sp/>setting<sp/>its<sp/>name,<sp/>defining<sp/>the<sp/>data<sp/>leaves<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>read<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>input<sp/>tree,<sp/>and<sp/>registering<sp/>the<sp/>particle<sp/>types<sp/>that<sp/>are<sp/>expected<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`~exp_mc20()`:<sp/>The<sp/>destructor<sp/>cleans<sp/>up<sp/>any<sp/>resources<sp/>allocated<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>exp_mc20_event_methods<sp/>Methods</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`event_template*<sp/>clone()`:<sp/>Creates<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>instance<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`void<sp/>build(element_t*<sp/>el)`:<sp/>Populates<sp/>the<sp/>event&apos;s<sp/>data<sp/>members<sp/>(event<sp/>number,<sp/>pile-up,<sp/>missing<sp/>transverse<sp/>energy,<sp/>etc.)<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>input<sp/>data<sp/>element.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`void<sp/>CompileEvent()`:<sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>core<sp/>method<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>class.<sp/>It<sp/>reconstructs<sp/>the<sp/>event<sp/>by<sp/>linking<sp/>the<sp/>various<sp/>particles<sp/>together.<sp/>This<sp/>includes:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Associating<sp/>top<sp/>children<sp/>with<sp/>their<sp/>parent<sp/>tops.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Linking<sp/>physics<sp/>truth<sp/>objects<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>parent<sp/>tops.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Linking<sp/>physics<sp/>detector<sp/>objects<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>parent<sp/>tops.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Matching<sp/>detector-level<sp/>objects<sp/>(jets,<sp/>electrons,<sp/>muons)<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>corresponding<sp/>truth-level<sp/>physics<sp/>detector<sp/>objects.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Vectorizing<sp/>the<sp/>particle<sp/>collections<sp/>for<sp/>easier<sp/>access.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>exp_mc20_event_particles<sp/>Particle<sp/>Collections</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>event<sp/>contains<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>particle<sp/>collections:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_tops`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>top<sp/>quarks<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_children`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>decay<sp/>products<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>top<sp/>quarks.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_physdet`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>physics<sp/>detector<sp/>objects.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_phystru`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>physics<sp/>truth<sp/>objects.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_electrons`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>electrons<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="35"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_muons`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>muons<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="36"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`m_jets`:<sp/>A<sp/>map<sp/>of<sp/>jets<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>After<sp/>`CompileEvent()`<sp/>is<sp/>called,<sp/>these<sp/>maps<sp/>are<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>populate<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>vector<sp/>collections<sp/>for<sp/>easier<sp/>access:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Tops`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="40"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`TopChildren`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="41"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`PhysicsTruth`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="42"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`PhysicsDetector`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="43"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Detector`<sp/>(a<sp/>combined<sp/>collection<sp/>of<sp/>jets,<sp/>muons,<sp/>and<sp/>electrons)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="44"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Jets`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="45"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Leptons`<sp/>(a<sp/>combined<sp/>collection<sp/>of<sp/>electrons<sp/>and<sp/>muons)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="46"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*/</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
    </programlisting>
